quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,Ea Hlohonolofetseng e be Eo Puso e leng Liatleng tsa Hae; Ea nang le Matla Oohle holima lintho tsohle
  67,2,"Eena Ea hlotseng Lefu le Bophelo, hore A tle A behe tekong mang le mango a lona ea boits’oaro bo nepahetseng. Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Ts’oarelang Khafetsa"
  67,3,"Eena Ea hlotseng maholimo a supileng ka tatelano: O tla bona tlholehong Ea Allah Ea Tletseng Lereko, kahoo sheba hape: O bona koli efe?”"
  67,4,"Talimisisa lekhetlo la bobeli: chalimo e tla boela ho uena e fifetse, e fokola, e khathetse"
  67,5,"Re khabisitse leholimo le ka tlase ka mabone, Re A entse likulo tse chalametsang ho leleka ea Mobe; Re ba hlophiselitse Kotlo ea Mollo o tukang"
  67,6,"Ba khesang Mong’a bona, ho teng Kotlo ea Lihele, e mpe pheletso"
  67,7,"Ha ba akheloa kahar’a ona, ba tla utloa mororo oa ona o ntse o tuka joalo"
  67,8,"O qhashoha ke khalefo. Nako le nako ha sehlopa se akheloa ka teng, ba lebeli ba ona ba tla botsa: “Ha ho ea ka ha fihla molemosi ho lona?”"
  67,9,"Ba tla re: “Ruri! Ho bile joalo, molemosi o ile a fihla ho rona; empa ra mo latola ka hore: “Allah ha A es’o ka a senola letho; u mpa u le phosong e ts’abehang.”"
  67,10,"Ba tla boela ba re: “Hoja re ile ra lemoseha kapa ra sebelisa kelello, Ruri! Re ka be re se har’a Balekane ba Khanare ea Mollo"
  67,11,"Joale bat la ipolela libe tsa bona, empa ts’oarelo e tla be e le hole le Balekane ba Khanare ea Mollo"
  67,12,"Haele ba ts’abang Mong’a bona ba sa ‘mone, ts’oarelo kea bona le moputso o moholo"
  67,13,"Ebang le pepesa lentsoe la lona kapa lea le pata, U na le tsebo e phethahetseng ea liphiri tsa lipelo tsohle"
  67,14,"Ha A ke ke A tseba-Eena Ea Hlotseng? Ke Eena Ea Utloisisang makunutu oohle, Ea Hlokolosi"
  67,15,"Ke Eena Ea hlotseng lefats’e ho nolofala, lebakeng la hau, kahoo tsamaea litseleng tsa lona, u je nala ea lona eo A u sitsitseng ka eona; Empa Tsoho e ho Eena"
  67,16,U ikutloa u sireletsehile hore Ea Maholimong A ke ke A etsa hore u metsoe ke lefats’e ha le reketla
  67,17,Kapa u ikutloa u sireletsehile hore Ea Maholimong A ke ke A romela Sefefo hore le tle le tsebe hore Temoso Ea Ka e joang
  67,18,"Empa ruri! batho pele ho bona ba latotse, joale e ile ea eba joang Tatolo Ea Ka"
  67,19,"Ha ba hlokomele linonyana kamoo li phukalatsang mapheo a tsona ka teng, li a khoale. Ha ho ope ea likakatletseng haese Ea TletsengLereko, Rurik e Eena Ea shebileng lintho tsohle"
  67,20,"Ke mang ea ka le thusang, le haele sesole, kantle ho Allah, Ea Tletseng Lereko? Mahana-tumelo ha ba ka har’a letho haese thetso"
  67,21,"Ke mang ea tlang ho le sitsa ka phepo, ha A ka khatla kabelo Ea Ha? Che, ba ngangaballa boikhohomosong le khelohong"
  67,22,"Ea tsamaeang a tiisitse hlooho, sefahleho sa hae se kebile, o tataisong e ntle,-Kapa ea tsamaeang ka makhethe Tseleng e Otlolohileng"
  67,23,"E re.” Ke Eena Ea le hlotseng, A sitsa ka kutlo, pono, boleng le kutloisiso: Empa teboho ea lona e ea fokola"
  67,24,"E re: “Ke eena ea le ngatafalitseng holim’a lefats’e, bohle le tla bokelloa ho Eena.”"
  67,25,"Ba ea botsa: “Ke neng ts’episo eo etlang ho phethahala haeba u bua ‘nete?”"
  67,26,"E re: “Tsebo ea nako e ho Allah A Inot’si, ‘Ke mpa ke le molemosi ea hlakileng.”"
  67,27,"Mohlang ba e bonelang hauts’oanyane, mahana-tumeloba ba tla sosobanya lifahleho, Ho tla thoe ho bona: “Sena ke seo le neng se bitsa.”"
  67,28,"E re: “Lea bona? Hore haeba Allah a ka ntimetsa hammoho le ba nang le ‘na, kapa A ts’ollela Mohau oa Hae holima rona, – joale ke mang ea tlang ho lopollaba Mahana-tumelo Kahlolong e mahlonoko?”"
  67,29,"E re: “U Tletse Lereko: Re kholoa ho Eena, re behile ts’epo ea rona ho Eena. Haufinyane le tla tseba hore na ke mang ea phosong e totobetseng.”"
  67,30,"E re: “Lea bona? – Haeba metsi oohle a lona a ka psha, ke mang ea ka etsang hore a kopotse lefats’eng"
  68,1,Nun. Ka pene le tlaleho e ngoloang
  68,2,Ka lereko la Mong`a hau ha u lehlanya
  68,3,Ruri! Moputso oa hau ke o sa feleng
  68,4,Tlholeho ea botho ba hau ke e babatsehang
  68,5,Haufi u tla bona le bona ba tla bona
  68,6,Hore na ke mang har’a lona ea hlanyango
  68,7,"Rurik e Mong’a hau Ea tsebang ka botlalo, ea khelohileng Tsela ea Hae: U tseba ka botlalo ba amohelang Tataiso"
  68,8,Kahoo se mamele bao ba latolang
  68,9,"Takatso ea bona ke hore u khelohe, hore ba tle ba khelohe"
  68,10,"Se natse mofuta oa motho ea nyonts’ang, – ea ikanang ka potlako"
  68,11,"Mofapanyi, ea tsamaeang a jala mashano"
  68,12,"Ea sitisang toka, ea tlolang meeli eohle, ea qoetseng sebeng"
  68,13,"Ea makoebeta, – ea silafetseng tlhahong"
  68,14,Hobane a sitsitsoe ka maruo le bara
  68,15,"Ha Lits’upiso tsa Rona li phetoa ho eena o re: “Lits’omo tsa mehleng ea khale.”"
  68,16,Haufi Re tla mo ts‘oea nko
  68,17,"Ruri! Re ba behile tekong joaloka ha Re ile Ra beha tekong Balekane ba Serapa, ha ba ne ba nka qeto ho khola litholoana e sa le hosasa"
  68,18,Empa ba se etse peheletso;(Ka Thato Ea Allah)
  68,19,"Eaba ho fihla moeti ho tsoa ho Mong’a hau, a hloekisa ba sa ile le sephume sa boroko"
  68,20,Kahoo Serapa hoseng sa tsoha eka sebaka se sets’o se shoeleng
  68,21,"Ha bosiu bo esa ba, ba bistsana ka bong’oe"
  68,22,“Eeang serapeng e sa le hosing ho khola litholoana.”
  68,23,"Ba tsamaea, ba hoeshetsa"
  68,24,“Le se lumelle mofutsana le ea mong ho kena ka har’a serapa kajeno
  68,25,"Ba qala letsatsi, ka qeto e khopameng"
  68,26,"Empa eitse ha ba bona serapa ba re: “Ruri! Re lahlehile"
  68,27,"Che, Re koaletsoe ka ntle"
  68,28,"E mong oa bona ea nang le toka a re: “Ha kea ka ka re ho lona le tlotlise Allah?”"
  68,29,"Ba re: “Tlotliso e be ho Mong’a rona! Ruri re ne re ntse re etsa bobe.”"
  68,30,"Ba fetohelana, ba qalella ho supana ka menoana, ba iphumana phoso"
  68,31,"Ba re: “Mehau ka rona! Re tlotse meeli e le ruri"
  68,32,“Mohlomong Mong`a rona U tla re neha se molemo ho feta sena. Hobane re retelehela ho Eena ka boinyatso.”
  68,33,"E joalo kahlolo. Empa e kholo kahlolo ea Bophelo Bo-tlang, – hoja ba ne ba tsebile"
  68,34,"Ruri! Sebakeng sa ba hloekileng ho teng lirapa tsa nyakallo, kapela Mong`a bona"
  68,35,Ana re ka ts’oara Batho-ba-Tumelo joalo ka Batho-ba-Sebe
  68,36,Molato ke eng ka lona? Le ahlola joang
  68,37,Kapa le na le Lengolo moo le ithutang teng
  68,38,Leo le tlang ho ba le tsohle tseo le ikhethelang tsona
  68,39,"Kapa le na le Selekane le Rona ka Kano, ho fihlela Letsatsi la Kahlolo, hore le tla fumana tsohle tseo le li batlang"
  68,40,Ak’u ba botse hore na ke mang har’a bona ea hlapanyang
  68,41,Kapa ba na le melingoana? Joale e re ba hlahise melingoana ea bona haeba ba buoa ‘nete
  68,42,"Letsatsi leo Tlhafu e tlang ho phetloa, e be ba ea bitsoa ho ithapalatsa ka lerato, Empa ba tla hloleha"
  68,43,"Mahlo a bona a tla be a talimile fats’e,-masoabi a ba aparetse; ha ba bona hore ba bilelitsoe pele-ho-nako ho tla ithapalatsa leratong, ba sa na le matla"
  68,44,"Ka hona ntese Ke Inots’i le bahanyetsi ba molaetsa ona: ka mekhahlelo Re tla lihela kotlo ho tsoa moo ba sa nahang"
  68,45,Ke tla ba ekeletsa nako. Ruri! Leano la Ka le Matla
  68,46,"Kapa u ba kopa moputso, kahoo ba tle ba imeloe ke moroalo oa sekoloto"
  68,47,"Kapa tse sa bonoeng li matleng a bona, hoo ba ka li ngolang fats’e"
  68,48,"Empa leta ka mamello taelo ea Mong`a hau, u se ke oa ts’oana le Molekane oa Tlhapi (Jonase) ha a ne a bokolla ke letsoalo"
  68,49,"Hoja Mohau oa Mong`a hae ha o oa ka oa mo fihlela, Ruri! A ka be a ile a lahleloa lebopong ka tlotlollo a tsotse"
  68,50,"Ka tsela eo Mong’a hae A mo khetha, A mo etsa e mong oa ba hloekileng"
  68,51,"Mahana-Tumelo ba ka batla ho ts’oasa ka mahlo ha ba utloa Moaletsa; ba re: Ruri ke lehlanya.”"
  68,52,"Empa ha se letho, haese molaetsa ho mafats’e ohle"
  69,1,‘Nete ea sebele
  69,2,‘Nete ea sebele ke eng
  69,3,Ke eng se tlang ho le hlokomelisa hore na ‘nete ea sebele ke eng
  69,4,Ba-Thamud le Ba-’Ad ba ile ba latola kotlo e tlang
  69,5,"Empa Ba-Thamud ba ile ba ripitloa ka sefefo sa lehalima le ‘mane, se ts`abehang"
  69,6,"Ba-`Ad, ba ripitliloe ka setsokotsane se bohale bo ts’abehang"
  69,7,"U ile A etsa hore se puputle masiu a supileng le matsatsi a robileng meno e ‘meli ka tatellano: kahoo u ka be u bone mofela oa batho ba tjapaletse, joaloka ha eka ke metso ea lifate tsa lipalema tse hlokang ‘moko li oele"
  69,8,Na u sa bona moneketsana feela oa bona
  69,9,"Le Faro, le ba bileng teng pele ho eena, le metse-moholo e repitliloeng, ka lebaka la Sebe"
  69,10,"Ba se mamele moromuoa oa Mong`a bona, kahoo A ba neha kotlo e matla"
  69,11,Re ile Ra u jara ka Areka mohlang metsi a neng a roaletse
  69,12,"Hore Re etse molaetsa ho uena, hore litsebe li-utloe, kelello e hopole"
  69,13,"Joale, mohla Terompeta e letsoang hang"
  69,14,"Lefats’e le tsitsingoang le lithaba tsa lona, li fetohang lerole hang, –"
  69,15,"Letsatsing leo, ketsehalo e tla phethahala"
  69,16,"Leholimo le tla aroha ka lehare, hobane letsatsing leo le tla be le fokola"
  69,17,"Manyeloi a tla be a le mahlakoreng a lona, a robeli a jarile terone ea Mong`a ka holim’a ona"
  69,18,"Letsatsing leo le tla biletsoa kahlolong, ha ho ketso le e ng`oe ea hau eo u e patang, e tlang ho pateha"
  69,19,"Joale ea tla nehoa tlaleho ea hae ka letsohong la molema, o tla re: “Nka, ba la tlaleho ea ka"
  69,20,“Ruri ke ile ka utloisisa hore tlaleho ea ka e tla mphihlela!”
  69,21,"Joale, o tla ba bophelong ba khotso"
  69,22,Serapeng se phahameng
  69,23,"Seo litholoana li leng haufi, li fihleleha"
  69,24,"“Ejang le noe, ka khotsofalo; ka lebaka la tseo le lirometseng nale, matsatsing a fetileng"
  69,25,"Ea tlang ho nehoa tlaleho ea hae letsohong la ntsohohlo, o tla re: “Jonna! Hoja ka se ke ka nehoa tlaleho ea ka"
  69,26,“Le hona ho hlokomela hore na tlaleho ea ka e eme joang
  69,27,“Hoja lefu ha lea ka la ntsometsa
  69,28,“Leruo la ka ha lena thuso ho `na
  69,29,“Matla a ka a felile!”
  69,30,"(Taelo e tla re)“Mo ts’oare, le mo tlame"
  69,31,“Le mochese Khanareng ea Mollo
  69,32,"“Le mo-khoantise a tlang`oe ka ketane, e bolele ba limitara tse mashome a supileng"
  69,33,“Enoa kea neng a sa kholoe ho Allah Ea Matla Oohle
  69,34,“A sa khothaletse phepo ea mafutsana
  69,35,“Kahoo ha ana motsoalle kajeno
  69,36,"“Kapa tsona lijo, ntle le ts’ila e hlatsoitseng maqeba"
  69,37,“E sa jeoeng ke ope haese baetsalibe.”
  69,38,“Ke le biletsa bopaking ka tseo le li bonang”
  69,39,“Le tseo le sa li boneng
  69,40,“Hore Ruri lena ke lentsoe la morumuoa ea hlomphehang
  69,41,"“Ha se lentsoe seroki: le kholoa hanyane"
  69,42,"“Kapa lona lentsoe la senohe: khalemo eo le e fumanang ke e fokolang"
  69,43,“Molaetsa o rometsoeng ho tsoa ho Mong`a Mafats’e
  69,44,“Haeba morumuoa u ne a ka iqapela lipuo Ka lebitso la Rona
  69,45,Ruri re tla moshakarela ka letsoho la hae la molema
  69,46,Ruri Re tla mo khaola mothapo oa pelo
  69,47,Ha ho mang oa lona ea ka mo sireletsang
  69,48,Empa ruri! Sena ke Molaetsa ho ts’abang Allah
  69,49,Re’a tseba hore har’a lona ho na le ba o hanyetsang
  69,50,Empa ruri Ke sehlabi ho Mahana-tumelo
  69,51,Empa ruri ke ‘Nete ea sebele
  69,52,"Kahoo, tlotlisang lebitso la Mong`a lona Ea Matla Oohle"
  70,1,Motsi o botsitse ka Kotlo e tlang ho oela
  70,2,"Mahana-tumelo, eo ho seng ea ka e qobang"
  70,3,E tsoang ho Allah Mong`a Litsela tsa Nyolohelo
  70,4,Tseo manyeloi le Khabariele a nyolohelang ho Eena ka letsatsi leo tekanyo ea lona e ka bang likete tse mashome a mahlano a lilemo
  70,5,"U mamelle, – ka Mamello e hlokang khoao"
  70,6,Ruri! Letsatsi ba le bonela thoko haholo
  70,7,Empa Re le bonela haufinyane
  70,8,Letsatsi leo ka lona leholimo le tlang ho ho ba joalo ka lesheleshele la koporo
  70,9,Lithaba li tla ts’oana le boea
  70,10,Ha ho motsoalle ea tla botsa ka motsoalle oa hae
  70,11,Le hoja ba tla be ba filoe pono ea hore ba bonane. Takatso ea moetsalibe; e tla ba e ka a ka itokolla Kahlolong ea Letsatsi leo ka ho itefella ka bana ba hae
  70,12,Ka mosali oa hae le ka ngoana’bo
  70,13,Kapa ka beng ka eena ba mo holisitseng
  70,14,"Le ka bohle ba teng mona lefats’eng, haeba ho khoneha ho mo lopolla"
  70,15,Empa che! Ruri! E tla be e le Mollo oa Lihele
  70,16,Khanare e qaqapollang lehata
  70,17,"E memang bohle ba khelohileng, ba furalla"
  70,18,Ba bokella maruo ba a khoaela
  70,19,Ruri! Motho o bopiloe a hloka mamello
  70,20,A phakisa a khopeha ha bomalimabe bo mo fihlela
  70,21,"Empa ha lehlohonolo le mo fihlela, oba leqe ka lona"
  70,22,Kantle le barapeli
  70,23,Ba tsitlaletseng thapelong ea bona
  70,24,Bao thepeng ea bona ho nang le litokelo tse fanoeng
  70,25,Malebana le mafutsana a kopang le ea hlolehang
  70,26,Ba kakatletseng ‘neteng ea Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  70,27,Ba ts’abang mesarelo ea Mong`a bona –
  70,28,Hobane Mesarelo ea Mong`a bona e khahlanong le Khotso le Boiketlo; –
  70,29,Ba bolokileng bohloeki ba bona
  70,30,"Kantle le basali ba bona le bao matsoho a matona a bona a ba ruileng, kahoo ba ke keba behoa molato"
  70,31,"Empa haele ba tlolang meeli eo, Ruri! bao e tla be e le batloli ba melao"
  70,32,Ka ho ts’oana le ba bolokang likano tsa bona le selekane sa bona
  70,33,Le ba its’etlehileng ka bopaki ba bona
  70,34,Hammoho le bohle ba hlokolosi lithapelong tsa bona
  70,35,Ruri! bana ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa tse hlomphehang
  70,36,Molato ke eng ka mahana-tumelo haele moo ba u tonetse mahlo
  70,37,Ka lehlakoreng le letona le le lets’eali ka mekhahlelo
  70,38,Ana motho e mong le e mong har’a bona o rata ho kena kahar’a Serapa sa Nyakallo
  70,39,"Che, Ruri! Re ba hlotse ka seo ba se tsebang"
  70,40,Ke ikana ka Mong`a ‘nqa tsohle tsa Bochabela le Bophirima hore re na le matla
  70,41,Ho beha ba betere ho ba feta sebakeng sa bona. Re ke ke ra hloloa
  70,42,"Kahoo, ba tlohele ho itaola le ho bapala ho fihlela ba kopana le letsatsi la bona leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  70,43,Eleng letsatsi leo ba tlang ho tsosoa mabitleng ka potlako joaloka ha eka ke litlholisano ho ea leseleng
  70,44,"Ka mahlo a ts’ohileng, ba bile ba aparetsoe ke masoabi: leo e tla be ele letsatsi leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  71,1,"Ruri! Re ile Ra romella Nooe ho batho ba habo: “Lemosa batho ba heno esere kahlolo e mahlonoko ea tloha ea ba oela holimo"
  71,2,"A re: “Oho batho ba heso! Ruri! Ke mohlokomelisi ea totobetseng ho lona"
  71,3,"“Hore le tlameha ho khumamela Allah le hona ho mo sebeletsa ka tieo, le nkutloe"
  71,4,"“Hore A tle A le ts’oarele libe tsa lona le hona ho lelefatsa nako ea lona ea pallo. Hobane Ruri! Nako eo pallo ea Allah e tlang, e ke ke ea liehisoa hoja le ne le tseba.”"
  71,5,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! Ke ne ke etsa pitso ho batho ba heso bosiu le mots’eare"
  71,6,Empa lipitso tsohle tsa ka ha li’a ka tsa thusa letho haese hona hore ba balehe ‘neteng
  71,7,"“Hobane ka linako tsohle ha ke ba bitsetsa hore U tle U ba ts’oarele, ba kiba litsebe tsa bona ka menoana le hona ho ipata lifahleho ka liaparo tsa bona; ba tsitlaletse nyefolong le hona ho ikhohomosa"
  71,8,“Ke ba hoelelitse ka lentsoe le phahameng
  71,9,“Ke ile ka phatlalatsa molaetsa pooaneng ho bona; ka etsa kopo ho bona sephiring
  71,10,"“Ke re: kopang ts’oarelo ho Mong`a lona. Hobane U Ts’oarela ka Mehla eohle"
  71,11,“Etsoe U tla le nesetsa lipula tsa litloebelele
  71,12,“A le ekeletse maruo le bara; A le sitse ka Lirapa le Linoka tse phallang
  71,13,“Molato ke eng ka lona haele moo le hloka ts’epo ho Allah molemong oa boits’oaro bo nepahetseng
  71,14,Empa e le Eena Ea le hlotseng ka mekhahlelo e fapaneng
  71,15,Na ha le bone kamoo Allah a hlotseng maholimo a supileng kateng ka tatellano
  71,16,A tsepamisa ngoeli ho ba khanya leholimong le lona letsatsi ho ba lebone
  71,17,“Ke Allah ea le hlahisitseng leroleng la lefats’e
  71,18,"“Pheletsong U tla boela A le busetsa ho lona hape, U tla le tsosa hape ka Letsatsi la Tsoho"
  71,19,“Allah U le aletse lefats’e
  71,20,“Hore le tle le hahlaule holim’a lona ka litsela tse pharaletseng.”
  71,21,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! ba ntatotse, eaba ba sala morao batho bao thepa le bana ba bona li sa tl’ong ho ba thusa ka letho haese Tahleho"
  71,22,“Ba lohile leqheka le ts’abehang
  71,23,"“Ba re: “Le se lahle melingoana ea lona kherehloa. E leng Wadd kapa Suw’a, le haele Yaghuth, Ya’uq kapa Nasr"
  71,24,"Ruri! Ba khelositse batho ba bangata tseleng, uena ha ho kamoo u ka putsang baetsalibe kateng haese ka ho kheloha.”"
  71,25,"Ba ile ba khamisoa metsi ho latela libe tsa bona, eaba ba akheloa Mollong. Ha ho bathusi ba ileng ba ba fumana ntle ho Allah"
  71,26,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! U se siee leha e le moneketsela feela oa moetsalibe lefats’eng"
  71,27,"Hobane haeba U ka ba siea, ba tla khelosa makhabunyane a Hau le tsoala tsa bona e tla ba baetsalibe"
  71,28,"Mong`a ka! U nts’oarele ‘moho le batsoali ba ka le ba-kholoang bohle ba keneng lelapeng la ka, banna le basali, U se ke oa putsa baetsalibe ka letho haese timelo"
  72,1,"E re: “Ke senoletsoe hore sehlopha sa Li-jinn li ne li thehile tsebe ho mamela[Qur`an], tsa re: “Re fela re utloile palo e babatsehang"
  72,2,"“E tataisetsa tokeng, re khotsoe ka hona: ha re na ho kopanya mong le mong le Mong`a rona"
  72,3,"“Bo phahame Botlotlehi ba Mong`a rona: ha A na molekane kapa mora"
  72,4,"“Ho ne ho ena le maoatla har’a rona, ba neng ba tloaetse ho buoa mashano a matala ka Allah"
  72,5,“Empa rea lumela hore motho kapa moea ha ba na tokelo ea ho bua leshano ka Allah
  72,6,"“Ruri! Ho teng batho, ba batlang ts’ireletso ho Li-Jinn, empa li ba ekelelitse phosong"
  72,7,"“Ba nahana joaloka uena, hore Allah ha ana ho tsosa ope bafung –"
  72,8,“Re ile ra leka ho phahlolla makunutu a leholimo; empa ra fumana le lebetsoe ke balebeli ba matla le malakabe a mollo
  72,9,"“Re ne re lula re larile, ho utsoa; empa ke mong le mong ea neng a leka ho mamela u iphumana a lelekoa ke lelakabe le chalametsang"
  72,10,"“Ha re utloisisi hore na kotlo e lebisitsoe ho boohle lefats’eng, kapana Mong`abona Urerilehobatataisatselengnepahetseng"
  72,11,"“Ho na le ba bang hara rona ba lokileng, ba bang ba fapane: re latela litsela tse fapaneng"
  72,12,"“Empa re’a tseba hore re ke ke ra ferekanya merero ea Allah, kapa hona ho Mo ferekanya ka paleho"
  72,13,"“Haele rona, re utloang tataiso, re amohetse mang le mang ea kholoang ho `Mopi oa hae ha ana ts`abo, ea qhekanyetso kapa bohanyapetsi"
  72,14,"“Hara rona ho na le ba ithobelang Allah, le ba tsoang tseleng ea toka. – haele ba ithobileng –ba nkile tsela e topileng"
  72,15,"“Empa haele ba tsoapohang, ke libeso tsa Mollo-oa-Lihele"
  72,16,"“Haeba ba ile ba tsitlallela tseleng, Re ka be Re ba sitisitse ka pula tsa matlopotlopo"
  72,17,"“E le hore Re ba behe tekong. Empa mong le mong ea tla kheloha khopolong ea Mong`a hae, U tla mo otla ka kotlo e mahlonoko"
  72,18,"“Libaka tsa thapelo ke tsa Allah: kahoo le se bitse ho mong kantle ho Allah"
  72,19,"“Nakong eo lekhabunyane la Allah le emang ho Mo rapela, ba mo opela hare ka bongata"
  72,20,"E re: “Ke rapela Allah a Inotsi, ha ke Mo kopanye le mang kapa mang.”"
  72,21,"E re: “Ha ke na matla a ho le utloisa bohloko, kapa hona ho le tlisa tseleng e nepahetseng.”"
  72,22,"E re: “Ha ho ea ka nts’ireletsang khahlanong le Allah, kapa ho fumana sets’abelo kantle ho Eena,”"
  72,23,"“Mosebetsi oa ka ke ho phatlalatsa seo ke se fumanang ho tsoa ho Allah, ho phtlalatsa molaetsa oa Hae. Haele ba nyefolang Allah le moromuoa oa Hae: ba loketsoe ke lihele, ba tla phela moo kahosafeleng”"
  72,24,"Khabareng, ha ba bona tseo ba neng ba li ts’epistoe, – ka nako eo ba tla tseba hore na ke mang ea fokolang e le mothusi, ea eisehang ka lipalo"
  72,25,"E re: Ha ke tsebe hore na seo le neng le se ts’episitsoe se haufi, kapa Mong`a ka U hlophisitse nako e telele ea pallo malebana le eona"
  72,26,"Hobane ke Eena Ea tsebang tse sa bonoeng; ebile ha ho mang, kapa mang eo A mo senolelang sephiri sa Hae"
  72,27,"Haese ho moromuoa ofe, kapa ofe eo a khahloang ke Eena, joale ebe U hlomamisa balebeli (manyeloi) ho tsamaea kapel’a hae le kamor’a hae"
  72,28,"Hore a tle a tsebe hore e feela ba phatlalalitse melaetsa ea Mong`a bona. U bile U kopetse hare liketso tsohle tseo ba li etsang, U boloka tlaleho ea lintho tsohle"
  73,1,Oho uena ea its`opileng ka seaparo
  73,2,"Ema bosiu, empa e seng bosiu boohle"
  73,3,"Karolo ea bona, kapa ka tlase ho moo"
  73,4,"Kapa haholoanyane, o phete Qur`an ka tekanyo ea lentsoe butle"
  73,5,Haufi Re tla romela molaetsa oa bohlokoa ho uena
  73,6,"Ruri! Ho tsoha bosiu ho bohlokoa molemong oa taolo ea phefomoloho ea hau, e molemo haholo sebakeng sa Lentsoe"
  73,7,Ruri! Mots’eare le na le mesebetsi eo le e etsang
  73,8,Empa tsitlallela khopolong ea lebitso la Mong`a hau; ikitlaelletsa ho Eena ka pelo eohle
  73,9,"Mong`a Bochabela le Bophirima: ha ho `Mopi kantle ho Eena; ikhethele Eena feela e le mosireletsi oa hau"
  73,10,"U be le mamello ho seo ba se buang, o tlohe pela bona ka tlhompho"
  73,11,"U ntese ho sebetsana le ba nang le lintho tse khotsofatsang tsa lefats`e, ba latolang `nete; u ba nehe nyehlisetso ha nakoana"
  73,12,Re na le mahlahlela a boima le mollo o chesang
  73,13,"Le lijo tse khamang, le kotlo e mahlonoko"
  73,14,Ka Letsatsi le leng lefats’e le lithaba li tla tsukutleha. Le lithaba li tla fetoha qubu ea lehlabathe le qhalanang
  73,15,"Re le romeletse, moromuoa, eo e tla ba paki khahlano le lona, joalo ka ha Re ile Ra romella moromuoa ho Faro"
  73,16,"Empa Faro o ile a latola moromuoa, Re ile Ra mo nanola ka kotlo e boima"
  73,17,"Joale ha o latola Allah, o tla its’ireletsa joang ka letsatsi leo Bana ba tlang ho ba moriri o moputsoa"
  73,18,Mohlang leholimo le patsohang ka lehare? Ts’episo ea Hae e tla phethahala
  73,19,"Ruri! Sena ke keletso: kahoo, ea ratang, a nke tsela e eang ho Mong`a hae"
  73,20,"Mong`a hau U oa tseba hore o ne o ema karolo-bobeli e boraro ea bosiu, kapa karolo ea bosiu, kapa karolo ng`oe ea boraro, le ka ho ts`oana le karolo eaba nang uena. Empa Allah U lekanya bosiu le mots’eare, hore u tsebe ho boloka palo moo. Kahoo u retelehetse ka ho uena ka mohau: bala, likarolo tsa Qur`an ka mokhoa oo le ka etsang tse bonolo. U tsebe ka botlalo hore ho ka `na haeba ba fokolang bophelong hara lona; ba bang ke bahahlauli, ba tsomana le nala ea Allah, ha ba bang ba loana tseleng ea Allah, bala Qur`an ka mokhoa oo le ka khonang; le rapele kamehla, le fane ka nyehelo; le alime Allah, kalimo e ntle. Etsoe botle bohle boo le bo romelang nale sebakeng sa phefomoloho ea lona le tla bo fumana kapela Allah; Eea, bo phahame ka moputso, le batle Lereko la Allah; Allah U Ts’oarela-khafetsa, U Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  74,1,Oho uena ea ikhatlileng
  74,2,Tsoha u fane ka temoso
  74,3,U rorise Mong`a hau
  74,4,Liaparo tsa hau u li hloekise
  74,5,U nene tsohle tse mpe
  74,6,"Kapa phanong ea hau, oa labella kuno"
  74,7,"Empa u be le mamello, u tsitlalle tseleng ea Mong`a hau"
  74,8,"Qetellong, ha Terompeta e lla"
  74,9,Leo e tlaba Letsatsi; Letsatsi la mahlomola
  74,10,Le seng bonolo ho ba se nang tumelo
  74,11,"Ntese, le eo ke mo hlotseng Ke Inots’i"
  74,12,Eo Ke mo sitsitseng ka melemo e fetang tekano
  74,13,Le bara ho ba pela hae
  74,14,Eo ke mo nolofalelitseng bophelo
  74,15,Empa o meharo hore ke mo ekeletse
  74,16,"Che, ho lits`opiso tsa Rona o khopame"
  74,17,Haufinyane Ke tla mo lahlela Mollong-oa-Lihele
  74,18,"U nahanne, a loha maqiti; –"
  74,19,Sekhobo se be ho eena; kamoo a lohileng maqiti
  74,20,"Ee, sekhobo se be ho eena; kamoo a lohileng maqiti! –"
  74,21,Eaba o oa qamaka
  74,22,"Eaba o busa lifahleho, o oa koata"
  74,23,Eaba o furalla ka boikhants’o
  74,24,"Eaba o re: “Sena ha se letho haese boloi, ba mehleng ea khale"
  74,25,Sena ke lentsoe la motho.”
  74,26,Hahufinyane! Ke tla mo lahlela Mollong oa Lihele
  74,27,Ke`ng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na Mollo-oa-Lihele ke eng
  74,28,"Ha o lumelle letho ho phela, le hona ho tlohela feela! –"
  74,29,O nts`ofatsa le ho fetola `mala oa motho
  74,30,Holima ona hona le ba leshome le metso e robong
  74,31,"Ha ho ope ntle le manyeloi joalo ka ba hlokomeli ba mollo; palo e tsepamisitsoeng e le teko ho mahana-tumelo, – hore batho ba Lengolo ba tle ba fihlele qeto, le ba-kholoang ba eketse ho tiisa tumelong; – ba nang le khoao ba tlohetse Batho- ba-Lengolo le ba-kholoang, le bao pelong tsa bona ho nang le maloetse le mahana-tumelo ba ka`na ba re: “E be Allah U bolelang ka papiso ee?” Allah U khelosa ea ratoang ke Eena, U tataisa ea ratoang ke Eena: ha ho ea ka tsebang ka matla a Mong`a hau, kantle ho Eena. Sena ke molaetsa ho batho"
  74,32,"Che, Ruri; ka ngoeli"
  74,33,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  74,34,Le ka meso ha mafube a hlaha
  74,35,Sena empa e le se seng sa lits’upiso tse kholohali
  74,36,Temoso ho batho
  74,37,Ho e mong le e mong oa lona ea khethang tsela e nepahetseng
  74,38,Phefomoloho ka ngoe e tla paka liketso tsa eona
  74,39,Kantle le balekane ba letsoho la molema
  74,40,"Lirapeng: ba tla botsana"
  74,41,Ba botse baetsalibe
  74,42,“Ke eng se le isitseng Mollong-oa-Lihele?”
  74,43,"Ba tla re: “Re bile sieo ho ba neng ba rapela”"
  74,44,“Kapa ba neng ba fepa mafutsana
  74,45,“Re ne re le mokhatlong oa basomi
  74,46,“Re ne re latola Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  74,47,“Ho fihlela lefu le re oela holimo.”
  74,48,Ha ho na ‘muelli ea tla bang molemo ho bona
  74,49,Joale molato ke eng ka bona hobane ba ile ba furalla temoso
  74,50,Joaloka ha eka ke lipokola li ts’ohile
  74,51,Li baleha tau
  74,52,"Mehlolo, mong le mong o batla ho fuoa maqhepe a manolotsoeng"
  74,53,"Che, ha ba na letsoalo la Bo-tlang"
  74,54,"Che, Ruri sena ke temoso"
  74,55,Mong le mong ea nang le hona a inkele temoso
  74,56,"Empa ha ho mong ea tla e boloka ka khopolo, kantle ho thato ea Allah: ke Mong`a Botlehali, le tsoarelo"
  75,1,Ka Letsatsi la Tsoho (ea bafu)
  75,2,Le ka phefomoloho e tletseng boinyatso
  75,3,Motho ha a hopole hore Re ka kopanya masapo a hae
  75,4,"Che, Re na le matla a ho kopanya menoana ea hae ka tatellano"
  75,5,Empa motho o lakatsa ho etsa bobe ka nako e ka pela hae
  75,6,"O a botsa: “Letsatsi la tsoho le neng?”"
  75,7,"Khabareng, mohla pono e fifalang"
  75,8,Ngoeli li fifalang
  75,9,Letsatsi le ngoeli li kopangoang
  75,10,"Ke letsatsi leo motho a tla re: “Sets`abelo sa ka se ho kae?”"
  75,11,Che! Ha hona sets’abelo
  75,12,"Kapela Mong`a hau, letsatsing leo e tla ba sebaka sa phomolo"
  75,13,"Letsatsing le motho o tla bolelloa pale ea hae, le tsohle tse a li siileng morao"
  75,14,"Che, motho o tla paka khahlano le eena"
  75,15,Leha a ka leka ho its`ereletsa
  75,16,U se bule molomo oa hau u potlaketse qeto
  75,17,Ho ho Rona ho bona pokello ea eona le phatlalatso
  75,18,"Ha Re se Re e phatlalalitse, e latele"
  75,19,Ho ho Rona ho e hlalosa
  75,20,"Che, empa motho a rata bophelo bo fetang hang"
  75,21,A tlohela bophelo Bo-tlang
  75,22,"Letsatsing leo, lifahleho tse ling li tla be li khanya"
  75,23,Li talimme ho Mong`a tsona
  75,24,"Ha tse ling, letsatsing leo, li tla be lihloname, li soabile"
  75,25,Ka khopolo ea hore bomalimabe boo mahlonoko bo tlilo liheloa holima tsona
  75,26,"Ruri, ha phefomoloho e fihla ‘metsong"
  75,27,"Hoba le mohoo, “Ke mang moloi?”"
  75,28,O tla qeta hore ke nako ea karohano
  75,29,Leoto le tla kopang`oa le le leng
  75,30,Mohlang oo tsela tsohle lit la lebisa ho Mong`a hau
  75,31,"Ha a nyehela letho, le hona ho rapela"
  75,32,Empa o latotse `nete. A furalla
  75,33,A hoantela ho mehahabo ka boikhants’o bohle
  75,34,"Sekhobo se be ho uena, ee, sekhobo"
  75,35,"Hape sekhobo se be ho uena, ee, sekhobo"
  75,36,Motho o hopola hore o tla siuoa a sa laoloe
  75,37,Ene e se lerotholi la there e thakhintsoeng
  75,38,Eaba o fetoha lehloele; eaba Allah U `mopa ho mo neha sebopeho
  75,39,"A `mopa ka bobeli, monna le mosali"
  75,40,Ha se Eena A nang le matla a ho phelisa bafu
  76,1,Ho ne ho se motsotso oo motho e ne e se letho le ka hopoloang
  76,2,"Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka lerotholi la tere, e le ho ‘meha tekong: Ra mo neha kutlo le pono"
  76,3,Ra mo bonts’a tsela; hore a lebohe kapa a hloke teboho
  76,4,"Mahana-tumelo Re a hlophiselitse liketane, lijoko le Mollo"
  76,5,"Ba lokileng, ba tla noella mopotjoaneng, o kopantsoeng le kafur"
  76,6,"Selibeng seo makhabunyane a Allah a noang ho sona, se ts’akhunyang ka matlopotlopo"
  76,7,"Ba phethisa likano, ba ts`aba letsatsi leo bobe ba lona bo tlang ho jaleha ka bophara"
  76,8,"Ba fepa mafutsana, likhutsana, le ba ts’oaruoa, leratong la Allah"
  76,9,"[ba re] “Re le fepa ka lereko la Allah Ea Inots`i: Ha re`a lebella moputso kapa tsona liteboho ho lona"
  76,10,Re ts’aba letsatsi leo ka lona khalefo ea Mong`a rona e tla beng e tlokoma.”
  76,11,"Empa Allah u tla ba lopolla bomalimabeng ba letsatsi leo, A ba khants`etse ka botle le nyakallo"
  76,12,"Hobane ba ne ba ena le mamello ba tsitlalletse, u tla ba putsa ka serapa le silika"
  76,13,"Ba tla phomola Literoneng tse phahameng, ba ke ke ba bona mocheso oa letsatsi kapa serame se hlabang"
  76,14,"Meriti e tlaba haufi le bona, liririella tsa litholoana li tla atamela pela bona ka ho ithoba"
  76,15,Har’a bona ho tla feta lijana tsa silivera le mepotjoana ea krystal
  76,16,"Tse khanyang sa khalase, tse entsoeng ka silivera: li tla lekanya litabatabelo tsa bona"
  76,17,Ba tla nehoa mopotjoana o kopantsoeng le zanjabil
  76,18,Seliba se bitsoang Salsabil
  76,19,"Ba tla feptjoa ke morolo o mosesane o sa tsofaleng; ha u ba bona, u tla nahana hore ke liperela tse qhalaneng"
  76,20,"E tla re ha u sheba, ke moo o tlang, ho bona khotso le sebaka se botlehali"
  76,21,"Ba tla be ba apere liaparo tse tala tsa silika le brocade, ba roetse lipetja tsa silivera; Mong`a bona U ba neha veine e hloekileng e halalelang ho noa"
  76,22,"“Ruri! Sena ke moputso oa lona, le ts`ebetso ea lona e amohetsoe.”"
  76,23,Ke rona ba rometseng Qur`an ho lona ka mekhahleho
  76,24,Kahoo ebang le mamello ka tsitlallelo ho taelo ea Mong`a lona le se mamele baetsalibe le banyefoli har`a bona
  76,25,Tlotlisa lebitso la Mong`a hau hoseng le mantsiboea
  76,26,"Le karolong ea bosiu, Mo khumamele, u Mo tlotlise bosiu bohle"
  76,27,"Haele bana, ba rata bophelo ba lepotla-potla, ba itebatsa letsatsi le mahlonoko"
  76,28,"Ke Rona ba ba hlotseng, Ra matlafatsa linoka tsa bona; empa, ha Re rata, Re ka ba fapanyetsana ka ba bang ba ts’oanang le bona"
  76,29,"Sena ke temoso: ea ratang, a inkele tsela e eang ho Mong`a hae"
  76,30,"Empa ha u ke ke, kantle ho thato ea Allah: hobane Allah U na le tsebo e phahametseng, U Seli"
  76,31,"U tla amohela mohaung oa Hae ea ratoang ke eena; empa baetsalibe, – U ba hlophiselitse kahlolo e mahlonoko"
  77,1,Ka liphefo tse romelloang ka tatellano
  77,2,Tse foqohang ka matla
  77,3,Lijala hole le haufi
  77,4,Li arole se seng ho se seng
  77,5,Li phatlalatse molaetsa hoohle
  77,6,Oa topollo kapa oa temoso
  77,7,Ruri! Seo le se ts’episitsoeng se tla phethahala
  77,8,Mohla linaleli li fifalang
  77,9,Leholimo le petsoha ka lehare
  77,10,Lithaba li qhalahangoa se ka lerole
  77,11,Le baromuoa ba khobokang’oang pallong ea bona –
  77,12,Ke letsatsi lefe la tsee tse boleloang
  77,13,Ke tsa Letsatsi la Tlhopho
  77,14,Ke`ng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na letsatsi la tharollo ke eng! –
  77,15,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,16,Ha Re ea ka Ra ripitlila meloko ea mathomo
  77,17,Le ka e latelang ho moo Re tla etsa joalo
  77,18,Re sebetsa joalo ka baetsalibe
  77,19,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,20,Ha Re’a u hlola ka lero le eisehang
  77,21,Ra le beha sebakeng sa phomolo ka tsepamo
  77,22,Ka nako e baliloeng
  77,23,Hobane Re ea hlopha; Re hlopha ka pabatseho
  77,24,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,25,Ha Re ea hlola lefats’e ho ba tulo
  77,26,Ho tse phelang le tse shoeleng
  77,27,"Ra hlola lithaba ho tsepama, tse phahameng; Ra le sitsa ka metsi a hlabosang"
  77,28,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,29,"[ho tla thoe] “Tlohang mona ho seo le neng se latola ka ho se shanofatsa"
  77,30,“E eang moriting o menahaneng ha raro
  77,31,"“Oo ho senang ho phola, o se nang thuso lebataneng la mocheso"
  77,32,“Ruri! O tlola mollo e le qhobosheane
  77,33,“Joaloka ha eka ke likamele tse ts’ehla.”
  77,34,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,35,Ke letsatsi leo ho senang ea tla beng a tseba ho buoa
  77,36,Kapa ho lumelloa ho ipuella
  77,37,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,38,Leo e tla be e le letsatsi la tlhopho! Re tla le khobokanya ‘moho le meloko e tlileng pele ho lona
  77,39,"Joale, haeba le na le leqheka, nqhekanyetseng"
  77,40,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,41,"Haele ba lokileng, ba tlaba tlasa moriti le pela liliba"
  77,42,"Le litholoana, – sohle seo ba se labalabelang"
  77,43,"“E jang le noe le khotsofale: seo le se sebelelitseng.”"
  77,44,Ke kamoo Re putsang ba etsi ba tse ntle kateng
  77,45,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ’nete letsatsing leo
  77,46,Ejang le nyakalle ha nakoana. Ruri! Leba etsalibe
  77,47,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,48,"Ha ho thoe ho bona: “Khumamang!” Ha ba etse joalo"
  77,49,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba nnete letsatsing leo
  77,50,"Ke molaetsa ofe ka morao ho moo, ba tlang ho o kholoa"